      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW NICKARA (4) filled a minor placing last start at Traralgon behind Devon Daisies (20.21) in a T3 Grade 6. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Can find winning form. PAW VITALI (6) turned in a plain run last time when seventh at Warrnambool over 390m behind Radiate (23.28) in a Bottom Up - Grade 6. Expected to feature in the finish. CHIC IN PARIS (1) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing seventh at Healesville, but was among the placings at this track three back. Can hit the frame this time. BONNIE BEAUTIFUL (8) looks a chance coming off a five weeks layoff.",
